values:
Yay, its Fall Break!

Friday i went home with Chet after school .. mm that was fun! Um.. Then we went to Mikes Game .. (RBP) and then to Gators .. haha i had so much fun there!

Saturday i did slept in the 12 .. then basically layed around the house the whole day.

Sunday was alright, i went out to lunch.. Crazy Buffet. I tried sushi .. YUCK! I got some bright pink tights .. for halloween!

Monday Chet came over .. wow, haha i had ALOT of fun .. You -- Twice hahah :) Im good. Um.. Aw, i fell asleep on him .. i seriously.. i can see me falling asleep in his arms forever.

Tuesday we went to wet n wild .. Me chet my sister and her friend. Hah it was sucha crappy day .. we got there at like 9 and it was cold and rainy.. so we walked to Starbucks .. mm, i got a French Vanilla Latte. Yum! Then after theat we went to Wet n' Wild. Haha Hey chet, REMEMBER the ELEVATOR =) =) =) + + + haha.. He got me a ring .. with a "C" in the middle. Its pretty!

Today i did nothing. My mom is getting lasor surgery on her face. Tomorrow Chets coming over Friday i might get my nails done with my mom..

Saturday is Kristinas party .. but im not sure if i want to go. Id rather go to the beach :D. sorry.. well, not really. I dont know! And Sunnnnnnday .. Nothing!

Oh and i applied to Publix!
